#61 Fool-Falco: Falco/?
Monster Rancher Metropolis: Monster Rancher DS Archive (DS): Japanese DS Games Archive: Monster Farm DS: Monster Regeneration List: Falco: #61 Fool-Falco: Falco/?
There are two versions of this monster, regular & large. Early on, the Fool-Falco you make will be 'regular'. Once your house is at level 2 you can find an item called the ancient relief #2, found at the Promiass ruins (pyramid venture).
